vocabInfos.mediumDef:
1) to slip off, drop off, clear away, draw off
1a) (Qal)
1a1) to slip or drop off
1a2) to draw off
1a3) to clear away
1b) (Piel) to clear out completely, clear entirely
vocabInfos._es_Definition: (a) qal   quitar, sacar; (b)   echar; (c)   caer de; (d) pi.   echar, desterrar

1) 脫掉, 脫落, 脫下, 清除

1b) (Piel) 徹底清除掉, 完全清除 #王下 16:6|
